OL,5, Lionel Messi has highlighted his       
OL,6, "special" ties with China, as he       
OL,7, continues to face anger from Chinese   
OL,8, fans for missing a game in Hong Kong.  
OL,10,FIn a video on social media site Weibo, 
OL,11,FMessi maintained an injury had led him 
OL,12,Fto sit out the match on 4 February.    
OL,14,FMessi played in Japan just days after  
OL,15,Fthat Hong Kong friendly, enraging fans 
OL,16,Fin China, where he is hugely popular.  
OL,18,FThe backlash against the 36-year-old   
OL,19,FArgentine superstar has dragged on for 
OL,20,Fweeks.                                 
